    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "I review ~15 PRs a week. The 400+ line diffs from junior devs are what kill me."
    },
    {
      "role": "interviewer",
      "text": "You mentioned \"I review ~15 PRs a week. The 400+ line diffs from junior dev…\" — that's helpful. Can you say more about existing summarization tools tried?"
    },
    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "I tried Graphite and CodeRabbit. CodeRabbit is noisy — I turned it off after a week."
    },
    {
      "role": "interviewer",
      "text": "You mentioned \"I tried Graphite and CodeRabbit. CodeRabbit is noisy — I tur…\" — that's helpful. Can you say more about moment of highest frustration in a review?"
    },
    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "When I'm context-switching mid-PR and lose the thread of what the change is actually about."
    },
    {
      "role": "interviewer",
      "text": "You mentioned \"When I'm context-switching mid-PR and lose the thread of wha…\" — that's helpful. Can you say more about willingness to install browser extensions?"
    },
    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "I have 40+ Chrome extensions already. It has to justify RAM and permissions to make the cut."
    },
    {
      "role": "interviewer",
      "text": "You mentioned \"I have 40+ Chrome extensions already. It has to justify RAM …\" — that's helpful. Can you say more about workflow integration expectations?"
    },
    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "It needs to live inside the GitHub PR page, not a separate dashboard. I won't open a second tab."
    },
    {
